{%- assign mail = settings.contact_email | default: shop.email -%}
<div class="prose rte">
  <p>
    Quick answers on shipping, returns, care, and sizing (from our customer documents). For full detail pages:
    <a href="{% render 'glazur-page-url', handle: 'shipping-returns' %}">Delivery &amp; returns</a>,
    <a href="{% render 'glazur-page-url', handle: 'care' %}">Care</a>, and
    <a href="{% render 'glazur-page-url', handle: 'size-guide' %}">Size guide</a>.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="faq-list">
  <div class="faq-item">
    <button type="button" aria-expanded="false">How does U.S. shipping work?</button>
    <div class="faq-panel">
      <p>
        Complimentary standard shipping on U.S. orders over $150 USD (before tax). Under $150 USD, standard shipping is a flat $10 USD (non-refundable). We ship from Boca Raton, Florida. Orders are typically processed in 1–3 business days and delivered in 2–5 business days after shipment. We use FedEx, UPS, and USPS; expedited options are available at checkout. Orders before 1:00 PM ET ship the same business day. Once placed, orders cannot be modified or combined.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button type="button" aria-expanded="false">Do you ship internationally?</button>
    <div class="faq-panel">
      <p>Yes, worldwide. Free international shipping on orders over $400 USD; otherwise rates are calculated at checkout.</p>
      <p>
        International orders ship via DHL Express, typically delivered in 3–7 business days. Duties and taxes may apply and are your responsibility unless prepaid at checkout. Duties, taxes, and shipping fees are non-refundable.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button type="button" aria-expanded="false">What is your return policy?</button>
    <div class="faq-panel">
      <p>Returns within 14 days of delivery. Items must be unworn, unwashed, in original condition, with all tags attached.</p>
      <p>
        Email
        <a href="mailto:{{ mail | escape }}">{{ mail | escape }}</a>
        within 14 days of delivery with your order number and return tracking number. Our team will send next steps.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button type="button" aria-expanded="false">What refund options do U.S. customers have?</button>
    <div class="faq-panel">
      <p>Store credit for the full item value, or refund to the original payment method with a $10 return fee. Original shipping is non-refundable. Returns are processed within 7–10 business days after we receive the item.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button type="button" aria-expanded="false">Can I exchange for another size?</button>
    <div class="faq-panel">
      <p>
        U.S. customers may request size exchanges subject to availability — contact
        <a href="mailto:{{ mail | escape }}">{{ mail | escape }}</a>. Exchanges are not available for international orders.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button type="button" aria-expanded="false">What about international returns?</button>
    <div class="faq-panel">
      <p>Returns accepted within 14 days of delivery. You pay return shipping. Refunds go to the original payment method only. Duties, taxes, and original shipping fees are non-refundable.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button type="button" aria-expanded="false">Are sale or final-sale items returnable?</button>
    <div class="faq-panel">
      <p>
        Items marked Final Sale or discounted 30% or more cannot be returned, exchanged, or credited. Price adjustments are only within 7 days of purchase and exclude sale items. Discount codes cannot be combined or applied to already discounted items.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button type="button" aria-expanded="false">How should I wash cotton and linen?</button>
    <div class="faq-panel">
      <p>
        Hand washing in cold water with a gentle natural detergent is best for delicates. Machine wash cold on delicate when appropriate; air dry when possible. Avoid bleach and harsh chemicals; wash lights and darks separately; iron on low–medium for linen.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button type="button" aria-expanded="false">How does Glazur fit?</button>
    <div class="faq-panel">
      <p>
        Our garments use a natural, feminine silhouette and typically run true to size. If you are between sizes, we recommend sizing up. Cotton and linen have little to no stretch — use our size guide or email for help.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button type="button" aria-expanded="false">Can I change or cancel an order after it is placed?</button>
    <div class="faq-panel">
      <p>
        Orders cannot be modified or canceled after placement. For edge cases, contact us at
        <a href="mailto:{{ mail | escape }}">{{ mail | escape }}</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button type="button" aria-expanded="false">What if my package is lost or delayed?</button>
    <div class="faq-panel">
      <p>
        We are not responsible for lost or delayed packages once marked as delivered. Orders forwarded through third-party services are not covered.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button type="button" aria-expanded="false">Who do I contact for help?</button>
    <div class="faq-panel">
      <p>
        Email
        <a href="mailto:{{ mail | escape }}">{{ mail | escape }}</a>
        — we’re happy to help with sizing, returns, and product questions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
